stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Synced
  Synced --> Drifting: target leaves hysteresis band
  Drifting --> Synced: drift clears before debounce
  Drifting --> Settling: debounce elapsed, emit ONE bounded action (capped, inline stop)
  Settling --> Settling: fill landed, keep converging toward target
  Settling --> Synced: reached target within band
  Synced --> Frozen: established position vanished (stop-out) while thumb still wants exposure
  Settling --> Frozen: stop-out detected mid-settle
  Frozen --> Frozen: thumb still pinned, refuse to re-open into the move
  Frozen --> Synced: throttle released to flat, re-arm
  Synced --> Degraded: link lost / oracle stale / ER-vs-guard divergence / market closed
  Drifting --> Degraded
  Settling --> Degraded
  Degraded --> Synced: degraded gate clears
